es.uvigo.darwin.prottest.util.collection
Class ParallelModelCollection

java.lang.Object
  es.uvigo.darwin.prottest.util.collection.ModelCollection
      es.uvigo.darwin.prottest.util.collection.ParallelModelCollection
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Model>, java.util.Collection<Model>, java.util.List<Model>
public class ParallelModelCollection
extends ModelCollection

A complex implementation of model collection, which is able to distribute whole set of substitution models amongst a certain number of groups, generally amongst the number of processors. This class is a composition of model collections, that will have disjunction and completeness properties.
